Deputy Senate President Ovie Omo-Agege has congratulated the Chairman of the Senate Committee Finance, Senator Olamilekan ‘Yayi’ Adeola, on his 50th birthday. In his message to Adeola, Omo-Agege said: “Over the years, you have remained a populist grassroots politician and philanthropist, utilizing your professional capacity, life experiences and resources for the betterment of your people”. He prayed God to grant  Adeola long life, peace, good health and enduring prosperity.